ews" Condemns the Action By Henry Umoru - Abuja President of the Senate, Senator Ahmad Lawan said on Friday that the recurrent attacks on schools and other acts of banditry across the country, call for intense soul searching on how the nation arrived at this very sorry situation. Lawan who condemned… February 26, 2021 In "News"